Release 0.2.2:
==============

Minor bug fix release. 

o KFontManager used to insert spurious empty line in the KDE fonts list.
  fixed
o Documentation now in sgml, html, dvi and ps format
o clean compile

Please read kfontmanager.html in the docs directory for information 
about KFontManger and its role in the KDE project.

